<subSubSection lastPageId="6" lastPageNumber="7" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="4.[151,1437,1792,1968]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[198,351,1904,1930]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">Description.</emphasis>
Head and pronotum black, shining. Antennae dark brown. Elytra black. Abdomen black with feebly blue reflex. Mandibles, maxillary and labial palpi and legs dark brown.
</paragraph>
<caption httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/197421/files/figure.png" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" targetBox="[250,1339,195,1768]" targetPageId="5">
<paragraph blockId="5.[151,1437,1813,1942]" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,274,1813,1837]" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">FIGURE 2</emphasis>
. 
<taxonomicName box="[287,552,1814,1837]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Gabrius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="breviantennatus" status="sp. n.">
<emphasis box="[287,552,1814,1837]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">Gabrius breviantennatus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis bold="true" box="[558,617,1813,1837]" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[558,617,1813,1837]" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" rank="species">sp. n.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
A, aedeagus, ventral view; B, median lobe of aedeagus (paramere removed), lateral view; C, underside of paramere; D, sternite IX of male; E, tergite X of male; L, sternite VIII of male. 
<taxonomicName class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Gabrius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="brevistrigatus" status="sp. n.">
